    "html": "<html lang=\"en\"><head>\n\t<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n\t<!-- style sheet that has stuff that is uniform on most pages-->\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/Physics/sitewide/standardstylings.css\">\n\n\t<!-- style sheet that has stuff that is unique to this program only-->\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"stylings.css\">\n\n\t<!-- loads JQuery into memory-->\n\t<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n\n\t<!-- loads javascript for standard things on site-->\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/Physics/sitewide/standardjavascript.js\"></script>\n\n\t<!-- loads javascript for this program only-->\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"javascript.js\"></script>\n\n\t<title>Jolly Gas Giant Problem</title>\n</head>\n\n\n\n<body onload=\"initialize();\">\n\t<div id=\"FullPage\">\n\t\t<div id=\"MainBody\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"ProgramTitle\" class=\"Titles\">Jolly Gas Giant Problem</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"OverviewSection\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"LabDirections\" class=\"Directions\">\n\t\t\t\t\tIn this program you will be trying to determine mass of the gas giant based on the period and orbital radius of the moon that you observe orbiting the planet.  Use the on screen ruler to get the orbital radius of the moon and time the moon for a least one revolution around the gas giant to determine the period of revolution.  Use this information to determine the mass of the gas giant<p>Click begin to work on this problem\n\t\t\t\t</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"PersonName\" class=\"Directions\"><span id=\"WordName\">Name:</span> <input type=\"text\" id=\"StudentName\" class=\"NameInput\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<img id=\"OverviewPicture\" src=\"images/OverviewPicture.png\" alt=\"Jolly Gas Giant Problem\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"BeginButton\" class=\"Button\" onclick=\"LoadIt()\">Begin</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"AvailableLanguages\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"LanguageTitle\" class=\"LittleDirections\" onclick=\"ShowLanguages()\">See Available Languages</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"LanguageDropDown\"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"LabSection\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"DrawingSectionOne\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<canvas id=\"CanvasOne\" width=\"925\" height=\"600\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tYour browser does not support HTML 5.0 Canvas...get a better browser!!!\n\t\t\t\t\t</canvas>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"SystemMessage\" class=\"Directions\">Use the ruler to get the radius of the moon's orbit and the timer to get the period of its revolution<p>Use these to get the mass of the gas giant</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"ToggleTools\" class=\"InvisibleButton\" onclick=\"ToggleTools()\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"ResetTimerButton\" class=\"InvisibleButton\" onclick=\"ResetTimer()\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"StopTimerButton\" class=\"InvisibleButton\" onclick=\"StopTimer()\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"SpaceForAnswer\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"AnswerTitle\" class=\"Directions\">Enter Answers</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"DirectionsforSub\" class=\"LittleDirections\">Don't include units</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"FormArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"FormRow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"TextBox\"><span id=\"Q1\" class=\"FormText\">Period (hours):</span></div><div class=\"AnswerBox\"><input type=\"text\" id=\"A1\" class=\"FormInputs\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"FormRow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"TextBox\"><span id=\"Q2\" class=\"FormText\">Velocity (m/s):</span></div><div class=\"AnswerBox\"><input type=\"text\" id=\"A2\" class=\"FormInputs\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"FormRow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"TextBox\"><span id=\"Q3\" class=\"FormText\">Mass (kg):</span></div><div class=\"AnswerBox\"><input type=\"text\" id=\"A3\" class=\"FormInputs\" placeholder=\"ex: 3.5e26\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"SubmitButton\" class=\"Button\" onclick=\"SubmitForm()\">Check</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\n</body></html>",
